title: Psycopg2 installation
---
body:

The short version
=================

First install the prerequisites (not needed on Windows, please adapt to your
\*nix distribution)::

    sudo apt install python3-dev libpq-dev

Then install the module::

    pip install psycopg2

The complete version
====================

For all the details, please check the `installation docs
</docs/install.html>`__.
